Big vision. Great Features.

12% Redistribution In BNB

12% of every buy/sell is taken and redistributed to all AK holders. Hold AK tokens, earn BNB. Minimum 10,000 tokens

Auto Paid Every 30 Minutes

You don’t need to claim your earned BNB. It’s automatically sent to your wallet every 30 minutes.

3% Liquidity Pool

3% of every transaction is transformed into liquidity for Pancakeswap.
It’s automatic and helps create a price floor (stability).

Anti-Dump Lock & 3% Sell Fee

Sells are restricted to less than 0.1% of the total supply + extra 3% fee is applied to all sells. This will allow us to reduce swing-trading and break whales’ control.

Secured By Design

Initial Liquidity Provided will be locked with DXSALE for 1 year.
The contract is being audited by BSC checker before the presale.

Team Lead, Community Driven

We set up a marketing wallet
(5% of supply) to ensure our capability in supporting the team and marketing expenses in the upcoming months.

Being formed on the Binance Smart Chain. We are here to become the most profitable memecoin.

Our first target is to became the biggest BNB auto reward token.

Our second target is to bring our Kitties to the Moon and then shoot for the stars.

HOW TO BUY

  • Download & setup or TrustWallet Download Metamask (a crypto wallet in form of a browser extension) or TrustWallet (an app for your phone). After that you will have to add the Binance Smart Chain to your network-list. (Click here for a step-by-step tutorial)
  • Buy and send BNB to MetaMask Buy BNB on an exchange (i.e. Binance, Kraken, Coinbase etc.). Transfer the tokens to your MetaMask wallet address. BEP-20 addresses start with a "0x"
  • Head on to PancakeSwap and swap for $AK Click here to head on over to PancakeSwap or use this address TBA to select AK. Set the slippage tolerance to 16% (sometimes it may be a bit more, depending on how much demand there is)
  • View $AK and HODL Swap BNB for AK. Now you need to add AK to your MetaMask (Tutorial here) or Trust Wallet to view your $AK. Lastly HODL!
